description.plain:
Valentina Cytrynowicz, known professionally as valentina cy, is a model-turned-musician from Los Angeles, California.

Studying production with hitmaker Mike Posner, the FORD model found her sound of soulful vocals, tongue-in-cheek lyrics and organic production. Learning to produce back in 2018, Valentina asserts control over her sound by developing each track from scratch.

Also an active photographer, the singer-songwriter shoots each project, while her sister Marcella Cytrynowicz directs the accompanying videos. On May 1, 2019, Valentina released her debut EP “Unmanageable”. Described as a pure and soulful catharsis, the young songstress wrote and produced each song on the project.

In an interview with Vogue Magazine, Valentina stated:

It’s empowering being able to have this level of control over how I’m portrayed,” she says. “When you have an idea of what you want sometimes you’re the best person to [execute] that idea.
